## Key Concepts
- WebSocket scale and connection churn
- Backpressure propagation across gateway and bus
- Heartbeat/timestamp accuracy and liveness tuning
- Autoscaling strategies (Kubernetes/HPA, event-driven scaling)
- Test harnesses: k6/ws, Gatling, Locust

